8e9a","posts",["Map",11,12,40,41,68,69,99,100,131,132],"life/周末咖啡地图",{"id":11,"data":13,"body":22,"filePath":23,"digest":24,"rendered":25},{"title":14,"description":15,"category":16,"tags":17,"pubDate":21},"周末咖啡地图","记录那些值得反复光顾的咖啡馆","life",[18,19,20],"咖啡","生活","探店",["Date","2026-04-22T00:00:00.000Z"],"![Coffee](/images/coffee-shop.jpg)\n\n## 独立咖啡馆的魅力\n\n连锁咖啡解决的是效率问题，而独立咖啡馆解决的是情绪问题。\n\n## 我的收藏\n\n| 名字 | 位置 | 推荐理由 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 晓咖啡 | 老城区巷子里 | 手冲埃塞俄比亚，果香明显 |\n| 黑羊咖啡 | 大学旁边 | 环境安静，适合带电脑 |\n| 星期八 | 文创园 | 甜品搭配很用心 |\n\n> 好的咖啡馆不需要太多理由，坐下来就知道了。","docs/life/周末咖啡地图.md","b093e6ebdcb7fff9",{"html":26,"metadata":27},"\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"/images/coffee-shop.jpg\" alt=\"Coffee\">\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"独立咖啡馆的魅力\">独立咖啡馆的魅力\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>连锁咖啡解决的是效率问题，而独立咖啡馆解决的是情绪问题。\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"我的收藏\">我的收藏\u003C/h2>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>名字\u003C/th>\u003Cth>位置\u003C/th>\u003Cth>推荐理由\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>晓咖啡\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>老城区巷子里\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>手冲埃塞俄比亚，果香明显\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>黑羊咖啡\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>大学旁边\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>环境安静，适合带电脑\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>星期八\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>文创园\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>甜品搭配很用心\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cblockquote>\n\u003Cp>好的咖啡馆不需要太多理由，坐下来就知道了。\u003C/p>\n\u003C/blockquote>",{"headings":28,"localImagePaths":34,"remoteImagePaths":35,"frontmatter":36,"imagePaths":39},[29,32],{"depth":30,"slug":31,"text":31},2,"独立咖啡馆的魅力",{"depth":30,"slug":33,"text":33},"我的收藏",[],[],{"title":14,"description":15,"category":16,"pubDate":37,"tags":38},["Date","2026-04-22T00:00:00.000Z"],[18,19,20],[],"life/极简主义实践笔记",{"id":40,"data":42,"body":49,"filePath":50,"digest":51,"rendered":52},{"title":43,"description":44,"category":16,"tags":45,"pubDate":48},"极简主义实践笔记","少即是多——从物品到思维的减法",[46,19,47],"极简","思考",["Date","2026-04-10T00:00:00.000Z"],"![Minimalism](/images/minimalism.jpg)\n\n## 起因\n\n搬家的那天，看着堆积如山的箱子，我开始认真思考：这些东西我到底用过几次？\n\n## 断舍离的三个原则\n\n1. **一年没碰过的，丢**\n2. **买替代品前，先断舍离**\n3. **不要为了\"可能用到\"而保留**\n\n## 效果\n\n断舍离三个月后：\n\n- *衣柜少了三分之二，每天选衣服不再纠结*\n- *书桌只留笔记本电脑和一盆绿植，专注力明显提升*\n- *手机 App 从 80 个减到 25 个，屏幕时间降了 40%*\n\n极简不是苦行，而是把精力留给真正重要的事情。","docs/life/极简主义实践笔记.md","493152d4e0eca823",{"html":53,"metadata":54},"\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"/images/minimalism.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalism\">\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"起因\">起因\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>搬家的那天，看着堆积如山的箱子，我开始认真思考：这些东西我到底用过几次？\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"断舍离的三个原则\">断舍离的三个原则\u003C/h2>\n\u003Col>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>一年没碰过的，丢\u003C/strong>\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>买替代品前，先断舍离\u003C/strong>\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>不要为了”可能用到”而保留\u003C/strong>\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ol>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"效果\">效果\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>断舍离三个月后：\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cem>衣柜少了三分之二，每天选衣服不再纠结\u003C/em>\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cem>书桌只留笔记本电脑和一盆绿植，专注力明显提升\u003C/em>\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cem>手机 App 从 80 个减到 25 个，屏幕时间降了 40%\u003C/em>\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>极简不是苦行，而是把精力留给真正重要的事情。\u003C/p>",{"headings":55,"localImagePaths":62,"remoteImagePaths":63,"frontmatter":64,"imagePaths":67},[56,58,60],{"depth":30,"slug":57,"text":57},"起因",{"depth":30,"slug":59,"text":59},"断舍离的三个原则",{"depth":30,"slug":61,"text":61},"效果",[],[],{"title":43,"description":44,"category":16,"pubDate":65,"tags":66},["Date","2026-04-10T00:00:00.000Z"],[46,19,47],[],"tech/astro-博客搭建指南",{"id":68,"data":70,"body":79,"filePath":80,"digest":81,"rendered":82},{"title":71,"description":72,"category":73,"tags":74,"pubDate":78},"Astro 博客搭建指南","从零开始用 Astro 搭建一个简洁高效的个人博客","tech",[75,76,77],"astro","博客","前端",["Date","2026-04-20T00:00:00.000Z"],"![Astro](/images/astro-blog.jpg)\n\n## 为什么选择 Astro\n\nAstro 是一个现代静态站点生成器，专为内容型网站设计。它的核心优势：\n\n- **零 JavaScript 默认** — 页面默认不发送 JS，加载飞快\n- **Islands 架构** — 按需水合，只有交互组件才加载 JS\n- **内容集合** — 内置 Markdown/MDX 支持，带类型安全的 frontmatter 验证\n- **多框架支持** — 可以混用 React、Vue、Svelte 等组件\n\n## 快速开始\n\n```bash\nnpm create astro@latest my-blog\ncd my-blog\nnpm run dev\n```\n\n## 部署\n\n- **Vercel** — `npm i vercel && vercel`\n- **Netlify** — 连接 Git 仓库自动部署\n- **GitHub Pages** — 使用 `@astrojs/github-pages` 适配器","docs/tech/astro-博客搭建指南.md","22d5c19404a3d2b0",{"html":83,"metadata":84},"\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"/images/astro-blog.jpg\" alt=\"Astro\">\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"为什么选择-astro\">为什么选择 Astro\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Astro 是一个现代静态站点生成器，专为内容型网站设计。它的核心优势：\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>零 JavaScript 默认\u003C/strong> — 页面默认不发送 JS，加载飞快\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Islands 架构\u003C/strong> — 按需水合，只有交互组件才加载 JS\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>内容集合\u003C/strong> — 内置 Markdown/MDX 支持，带类型安全的 frontmatter 验证\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>多框架支持\u003C/strong> — 可以混用 React、Vue、Svelte 等组件\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"快速开始\">快速开始\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cpre class=\"astro-code github-dark\" style=\"background-color:#24292e;color:#e1e4e8; overflow-x: auto;\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\">\u003Ccode>\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">npm\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> create\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> astro@latest\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> my-blog\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">cd\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> my-blog\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">npm\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> run\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> dev\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/code>\u003C/pre>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"部署\">部署\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Vercel\u003C/strong> — \u003Ccode>npm i vercel &#x26;&#x26; vercel\u003C/code>\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Netlify\u003C/strong> — 连接 Git 仓库自动部署\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>GitHub Pages\u003C/strong> — 使用 \u003Ccode>@astrojs/github-pages\u003C/code> 适配器\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>",{"headings":85,"localImagePaths":93,"remoteImagePaths":94,"frontmatter":95,"imagePaths":98},[86,89,91],{"depth":30,"slug":87,"text":88},"为什么选择-astro","为什么选择 Astro",{"depth":30,"slug":90,"text":90},"快速开始",{"depth":30,"slug":92,"text":92},"部署",[],[],{"title":71,"description":72,"category":73,"pubDate":96,"tags":97},["Date","2026-04-20T00:00:00.000Z"],[75,76,77],[],"tech/git-实用技巧",{"id":99,"data":101,"body":109,"filePath":110,"digest":111,"rendered":112},{"title":102,"description":103,"category":73,"tags":104,"pubDate":108},"Git 实用技巧","整理日常开发中常用的 Git 操作和技巧",[105,106,107],"git","工具","开发效率",["Date","2026-04-15T00:00:00.000Z"],"![Git](/images/git-tools.jpg)\n\n## 交互式变基\n\n```bash\ngit rebase -i HEAD~3\n```\n\n## 暂存工作区\n\n```bash\ngit stash           # 暂存\ngit stash pop       # 恢复并删除暂存\n```\n\n## 查找引入 Bug 的提交\n\n```bash\ngit bisect start\ngit bisect bad\ngit bisect good \u003Ccommit-hash>\ngit bisect reset\n```\n\n## 格式化日志\n\n```bash\ngit log --oneline --graph --all\n```","docs/tech/Git 实用技巧.md","db92c58bdab78f9d",{"html":113,"metadata":114},"\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"/images/git-tools.jpg\" alt=\"Git\">\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"交互式变基\">交互式变基\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cpre class=\"astro-code github-dark\" style=\"background-color:#24292e;color:#e1e4e8; overflow-x: auto;\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\">\u003Ccode>\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">git\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> rebase\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> -i\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> HEAD~3\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/code>\u003C/pre>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"暂存工作区\">暂存工作区\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cpre class=\"astro-code github-dark\" style=\"background-color:#24292e;color:#e1e4e8; overflow-x: auto;\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\">\u003Ccode>\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">git\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> stash\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#6A737D\">           # 暂存\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">git\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> stash\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> pop\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#6A737D\">       # 恢复并删除暂存\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/code>\u003C/pre>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"查找引入-bug-的提交\">查找引入 Bug 的提交\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cpre class=\"astro-code github-dark\" style=\"background-color:#24292e;color:#e1e4e8; overflow-x: auto;\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\">\u003Ccode>\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">git\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> bisect\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> start\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">git\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> bisect\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> bad\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">git\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> bisect\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> good\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\"> &#x3C;\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\">commit-has\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">h\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">git\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> bisect\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> reset\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/code>\u003C/pre>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"格式化日志\">格式化日志\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cpre class=\"astro-code github-dark\" style=\"background-color:#24292e;color:#e1e4e8; overflow-x: auto;\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\">\u003Ccode>\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">git\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> log\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> --oneline\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> --graph\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> --all\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/code>\u003C/pre>",{"headings":115,"localImagePaths":125,"remoteImagePaths":126,"frontmatter":127,"imagePaths":130},[116,118,120,123],{"depth":30,"slug":117,"text":117},"交互式变基",{"depth":30,"slug":119,"text":119},"暂存工作区",{"depth":30,"slug":121,"text":122},"查找引入-bug-的提交","查找引入 Bug 的提交",{"depth":30,"slug":124,"text":124},"格式化日志",[],[],{"title":102,"description":103,"category":73,"pubDate":128,"tags":129},["Date","2026-04-15T00:00:00.000Z"],[105,106,107],[],"tech/typescript-类型体操入门",{"id":131,"data":133,"body":140,"filePath":141,"digest":142,"rendered":143},{"title":134,"description":135,"category":73,"tags":136,"pubDate":139},"TypeScript 类型体操入门","掌握 TypeScript 高级类型，写出更安全的代码",[137,77,138],"typescript","编程",["Date","2026-04-18T00:00:00.000Z"],"![TypeScript](/images/typescript.jpg)\n\n## 基础泛型\n\n```typescript\nfunction identity\u003CT>(arg: T): T {\n  return arg\n}\n```\n\n## 条件类型\n\n```typescript\ntype IsString\u003CT> = T extends string ? true : false\ntype A = IsString\u003C'hello'>  // true\n```\n\n## 映射类型\n\n```typescript\ntype Readonly\u003CT> = {\n  readonly [K in keyof T]: T[K]\n}\n```\n\n## 实战：DeepPartial\n\n```typescript\ntype DeepPartial\u003CT> = {\n  [K in keyof T]?: T[K] extends object ? DeepPartial\u003CT[K]> : T[K]\n}\n```","docs/tech/TypeScript 类型体操入门.md","8f85ae4599e2fd5d",{"html":144,"metadata":145},"\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"/images/typescript.jpg\" alt=\"TypeScript\">\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"基础泛型\">基础泛型\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cpre class=\"astro-code github-dark\" style=\"background-color:#24292e;color:#e1e4e8; overflow-x: auto;\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"typescript\">\u003Ccode>\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">function\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\"> identity\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">&#x3C;\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">T\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">>(\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#FFAB70\">arg\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">:\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\"> T\u003C/s